description.narrative: This award strives to advance freedom and dignity by assisting governments and citizens to establish, consolidate and protect democratic institutions, processes, and values, including participatory and accountable governance, rule of law, authentic political competition, civil society, human rights, and the free flow of information. More specifically, this includes General Services (A,B,C). Administrative Expenses. This Contract (SAQMMA12C0117) is for Rapid Expert Assistance and Cooperation Teams services. All contract deliverables, correspondence and invoices for Option Year One will be accounted for under contract number SAQMMA13C0084..
